headline: PSEG To Announce First Quarter 2025 Financial Results On April 30
summary: Public Service Enterprise Group Incorporated (PSEG) will host its first quarter 2025 earnings call at 11:00 a.m. ET on Wednesday, April 30, during which management will discuss first quarter financial results, financial guidance, capital investments, regulatory activities, and other important matters.
